 to Thee according to Thy will, and receive from Thee the fulfillment of my supplications. {\ltrch\hich\fs20\i\loch\fs20\i Have mercy upon Thy Creatures and upon me, a great sinner.}}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f0\fs24\lang1033\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033 
